commit.message: Make UTF8ZipCoder.hasTrailingSlash private and remove the unused ZipCoder.hasTrailingSlash with the associated slashBytes() method and slashBytes field
Revert signature change in ZipFile.getZipEntry so iterators won't need to wrap arguments in as EntryPos instances
Revert change in access modifier for ZipCoder.checkedHash
Avoid repeated checking of trailing slash in ZipFile.getZipEntry
